      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:02:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Novavax 因安全性问题暂停流感和新冠疫苗研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/novavax-shares-plunge-after-fda-places-a-hold-on-its-flu-shots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一名研究志愿者出现严重的神经疾病，美国监管机构暂停了 Novavax Inc. 的实验疫苗研发，随后该公司股价下跌 19%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/novavax-shares-plunge-after-fda-places-a-hold-on-its-flu-shots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 13:39:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币逼近 70,000 美元，投机者瞄准创纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/bitcoin-approaches-70-000-with-speculators-eyeing-record-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对高风险资产和即将到来的美国大选的乐观情绪不断增强，比特币多头再次将目光投向了 3 月份创下的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/bitcoin-approaches-70-000-with-speculators-eyeing-record-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 13:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
